175
00:16:28,419 --> 00:16:30,286
我希望那不是我的马.
I hope that wasn't my horse.

176
00:16:30,322 --> 00:16:32,155
她做得很好.
She's doing well.

177
00:16:32,189 --> 00:16:34,190
她吃不下的.
She'll never keep it down.

178
00:16:34,226 --> 00:16:36,360
