Khalakka Dothrae!</i>

180
00:16:55,582 --> 00:16:55,648
<i>(王子骑着马!)
Khalakka Dothrae!</i>

181
00:16:57,616 --> 00:16:59,517
告诉我她在说什么.
Tell me what she's saying.

182
00:16:59,552 --> 00:17:02,054
"王子骑着马.
"The prince is riding.

183
00:17:02,087 --> 00:17:05,089
我听见他的蹄声隆隆.
I have heard the thunder of his hooves.

184
00:17:05,123 --> 00:17:07,525
他的马迅捷如风.
Swift as the wind he rides.

185
00:17:08,959 --> 00:17:11,829
他的敌人将在他面前颤抖...
His enemies will cower before him...

186
00:17:13,296 --> 00:17:16,800
敌人的妻子们将悲伤泣血."
And their wives will weep tears of blood."

187
00:17:20,538 --> 00:17:22,673
她将生下一个男孩.
She's going to have a boy.

188
00:17:25,410 --> 00:17:28,046
他不会是一个真正的坦格利安.
He won't be a real Targaryen.

189
00:17:28,081 --> 00:17:30,483
他不会是一条真龙.
He won't be a true Dragon.

190
00:18:20,869 --> 00:18:23,838
<i>(骑着世界的骏马!)
Vezh fin saja rhaesheseres!</i>

191
00:18:23,871 --> 00:18:26,974
"骑着世界的骏马."
"The stallion who mounts the world."

192
00:18:27,008 --> 00:18:30,011
那骏马将是卡奥中的卡奥.
The stallion is the Khal of Khals.

193
00:18:30,044 --> 00:18:33,147
他将统一所有的卡拉萨.
He shall unite the people into a single Khalasar.

194
00:18:33,181 --> 00:18:36,550
<i>全世界的人都将属于他.
All the people of the world will be his herd.</i>

195
00:18:36,584 --> 00:18:38,785
