199
00:18:49,198 --> 00:18:51,698
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

200
00:18:51,733 --> 00:18:53,868
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

201
00:18:53,901 --> 00:18:56,669
雷戈! 雷戈...
Rhaego! Rhaego...

202
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:05,410
他们爱戴她.
They love her.

203
00:19:08,014 --> 00:19:09,246
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

204
00:19:09,282 --> 00:19:12,016
雷戈! 雷戈...
Rhaego! Rhaego...

205
00:19:29,402 --> 00:19:32,505
今天她是一位真正的王后了.
She truly is a queen today.

206
00:20:00,798 --> 00:20:04,302
别让他们看到你在维斯多斯拉克带着剑.
Don't let them see you carrying a sword in Vaes Dothrak.

207
00:20:04,335 --> 00:20:06,469
你知道这违反律法.
You know the law.

208
00:20:06,504 --> 00:20:08,471
这律法管不着我.
It's not my law.

209
00:20:08,506 --> 00:20:10,475
它们不是属于你的.
They don't belong to you.

210
00:20:10,508 --> 00:20:12,910
她的东西都是属于我的.
Whatever is hers is also mine.

211
00:20:13,813 --> 00:20:15,581
或许曾经属于你.
Once, perhaps.

212
00:20:17,516 --> 00:20:20,352
如果我卖掉一颗龙蛋, 就足够买一条船.
If I sell one egg, I'll have enough to buy a ship.

213
00:20:20,387 --> 00:20:22,554
卖两颗... 一条船加一支军队.
Two eggs... a ship and an army.

214
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:25,891
- 你拿了三颗. - 我需要一支大军.
- And you have all three. - I need a large army.

215
00:20:27,262 --> 00:20:30,063
我是一个王朝复兴最后的希望, 莫尔蒙.
I'm the last hope of a dynasty, Mormont.

216
00:20:30,098 --> 00:20:32,233
世界上古往今来最伟大的王朝
The greatest dynasty this world has ever seen

217
00:20:32,266 --> 00:20:34,768
自五岁起我就担负着这项使命...
on my shoulders since I was five years old...

218
00:20:34,803 --> 00:20:37,804
却从没人给予我在那帐篷里他们所给予她的东西.
and no one has ever given me what they gave to her in that tent.

219
00:20:37,839 --> 00:20:39,707
从来没有.
Never.

220
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,975
一点也没有.
Not a piece of it.

221
00:20:42,009 --> 00:20:44,678
没有这些我如何能履行我的使命?
How can I carry what I need to carry without it?

222
00:20:44,711 --> 00:20:46,412
嗯?
Hmm?

223
00:20:46,447 --> 00:20:48,881
没有财富或恐惧或爱戴如何能进行统治?
Who can rule without wealth or fear or love?

224
00:20:53,218 --> 00:20:57,123
哦, 你站在那里, 又高贵又荣誉.
Oh, you stand there, all nobility and honor.

225
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:02,996
你以为我没发现你是用何种眼神看着我的妹妹, 嗯?
You don't think I see you looking at my little sister, hmm?

226
00:21:03,031 --> 00:21:05,566
你以为我不知道你想要什么?
Don't think I know what you want?

227
00:21:08,603 --> 00:21:11,506
我无所谓. 你可以拥有她.
I don't care. You can have her.

228
00:21:11,541 --> 00:21:13,808
她可以当蛮子的王后并且尽情...
She can be Queen of the savages and dine

229
00:21:13,843 --> 00:21:15,777
享用那最美味的马的器官,
on the finest bloody horseparts,

230
00:21:15,812 --> 00:21:18,613
你也可以尽情享用她的任何器官.
and you can dine on whichever parts of her you like.

231
00:21:19,948 --> 00:21:22,284
让我走吧.
But let me go.

232
00:21:24,452 --> 00:21:25,954
你可以走.
You can go.

233
00:21:25,987 --> 00:21:27,822
但你不能带走龙蛋.
You can't have the eggs.

234
00:21:27,855 --> 00:21:29,622
你曾向我宣誓效忠.
You swore an oath to me.

235
00:21:29,658 --> 00:21:32,159
忠诚对你来说不值一提吗?
Does loyalty mean nothing to you?

236
00:21:32,192 --> 00:21:34,361
那是我的一切.
It means everything to me.

237
00:21:34,394 --> 00:21:36,396
然而你还是站在这里.
And yet here you stand.

238
00:21:36,429 --> 00:21:38,531
所以我还是站在这里.
And yet here I stand.

239
00:21:54,482 --> 00:21:57,083
莫德!
Mord!

240
00:21:57,118 --> 00:21:59,352
莫德!
Mord!

241
00:22:01,755 --> 00:22:03,622
莫德!
Mord!

242
00:22:07,327 --> 00:22:09,361
莫德!
Mord!

243
00:22:10,363 --> 00:22:12,165
莫德.
Mord.

244
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:15,200
又在吵闹了!
Noise again!

245
00:22:17,604 --> 00:22:20,407
- 有关那些金子... - 没有金子!
- About the gold... - No gold!

246
00:22:20,441 --> 00:22:22,877
- 没有金子. - 听我说!
- No gold. - Listen to me!

247
00:22:22,910 --> 00:22:24,978
听我说.
Listen to me.

248
00:22:25,013 --> 00:22:27,215
有时候财产
Sometimes possession

249
00:22:27,248 --> 00:22:29,351
是个抽象的概念...
is an abstract concept...

250
00:22:31,388 --> 00:22:33,922
他们抓我的时候拿走了我的钱包,
When they captured me, they took my purse,

251
00:22:33,957 --> 00:22:35,925
但那些金子还是我的.
but the gold is still mine.

252
00:22:35,958 --> 00:22:37,727
在哪儿?
Where?

253
00:22:37,761 --> 00:22:39,861
在哪儿? 我不知道在哪儿,
Where? I don't know where,

254
00:22:39,896 --> 00:22:41,196
但等他们给我自由的时候...
but when they free me...

255
00:22:41,230 --> 00:22:42,631
你想要自由?
You want free?

256
00:22:43,565 --> 00:22:45,900
那儿有自由.
Go be free.

257
00:22:47,169 --> 00:22:49,336
你有没有听说过这句话
Have you ever heard the phrase

258
00:22:49,371 --> 00:22:51,304
"象兰尼斯特家一样有钱"?
"rich as a Lannister"?

259
00:22:53,909 --> 00:22:55,910
<i>你当然听说过!
Of course you have!</i>

260
00:22:55,944 --> 00:22:58,880
你是个聪明人.
You're a smart man.

261
00:22:58,913 --> 00:23:01,749
你知道兰尼斯特家.
You know who the Lannisters are.

262
00:23:02,651 --> 00:23:05,620
我就是兰尼斯特家的.
I am a Lannister.

263
00:23:05,654 --> 00:23:09,323
泰温之子提利昂!
Tyrion, son of Tywin!

264
00:23:09,359 --> 00:23:13,429
而且, 你当然也听说过这句话,
And of course, you have also heard the phrase,

265
00:23:13,464 --> 00:23:16,800
"兰尼斯特有债必还."
"a Lannister always pays his debts."

266
00:23:18,602 --> 00:23:21,170
如果你替我传个口信...
If you deliver a message from me...

267
00:23:22,273 --> 00:23:25,641
给艾林夫人, 就算我欠你一笔债.
to Lady Arryn, I will be in your debt.

268
00:23:27,410 --> 00:23:29,746
我会给你很多金子.
I will owe you gold.

269
00:23:31,115 --> 00:23:33,249
如果你传了口信
If you deliver the message

270
00:23:33,285 --> 00:23:37,121
如果我活下来了, 我一定会的.
and I live, which I very much intend to do.

271
00:23:39,757 --> 00:23:41,558
什么口信?
What message?

272
00:23:48,233 --> 00:23:50,868
告诉她我打算认罪.
Tell her I wish to confess my crimes.

273
00:23:57,243 --> 00:24:00,277
你打算认罪?
You wish to confess your crimes?

274
00:24:00,313 --> 00:24:01,947
是的, 夫人.
Yes, My Lady.

275
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,515
我愿意, 夫人.
I do, My Lady.

276
00:24:03,548 --> 00:24:06,884
天牢可以让任何人屈服.
The sky cells always break them.

277
00:24:06,919 --> 00:24:09,121
说吧, 小恶魔.
Speak, Imp.

278
00:24:09,156 --> 00:24:11,556
坦诚地面对诸神吧.
Meet your gods as an honest man.

279
00:24:16,361 --> 00:24:19,998
该从何说起呢, 各位大人和夫人?
Where do I begin, my lords and ladies?

280
00:24:21,301 --> 00:24:23,169
我是个坏蛋,
I'm a vile man,

281
00:24:23,202 --> 00:24:25,103
我承认这一点.
I confess it.

282
00:24:25,138 --> 00:24:28,140
我犯下的罪过数不胜数.
My crimes and sins are beyond counting.

283
00:24:28,175 --> 00:24:31,310
<i>我撒过谎骗过人...
I have lied and cheated...</i>

284
00:24:32,644 --> 00:24:34,779
<i>赌过钱嫖过妓.
gambled and whored.</i>

285
00:24:36,483 --> 00:24:38,450
<i>我不是特别擅长暴力,
I'm not particularly good at violence,</i>

286
00:24:38,485 --> 00:24:41,920
但我擅长鼓动他人替我施暴.
but I'm good at convincing others to do violence for me.

287
00:24:44,558 --> 00:24:46,692
我想你是想听具体一点的.
You want specifics, I suppose.

288
00:24:48,095 --> 00:24:50,631
七岁那年, 我看见一个女仆
When I was seven I saw a servant girl

289
00:24:50,665 --> 00:24:52,632
在河里洗澡.
bathing in the river.

290
00:24:52,668 --> 00:24:54,535
我偷走了她的衣服.
I stole her robe.

291
00:24:54,569 --> 00:24:56,902
于是她不得不...
She was forced to return to the castle

292
00:24:56,938 --> 00:24:58,938
光着身子哭着回城堡.
naked and in tears.

293
00:25:00,541 --> 00:25:02,274
如果我闭上眼睛,
If I close my eyes,

294
00:25:02,308 --> 00:25:05,511
还能看见她跳动的乳头.
I can still see her tits bouncing.

295
00:25:07,779 --> 00:25:12,015
十岁那年, 我在我叔叔的靴子里塞满羊粪.
When I was 10 I stuffed my Uncle's boots with goatshit.

296
00:25:12,051 --> 00:25:14,451
<i>别人问我的时候,
When confronted with my crime,</i>

297
00:25:14,486 --> 00:25:16,955
我归咎于一个侍从. 那可怜孩子挨了鞭打
I blamed a squire. Poor boy was flogged

298
00:25:16,988 --> 00:25:19,224
而我却逃脱了惩罚.
and I escaped justice.

299
00:25:19,257 --> 00:25:21,025
<i>十二岁那年
When I was 12</i>

300
00:25:21,060 --> 00:25:24,062
我朝一锅炖海龟猛挤我那小鳗鱼...
I milked my eel into a pot of turtle stew.

301
00:25:24,096 --> 00:25:27,132
猛扭我那小独眼蛇...
I flogged the one-eyed snake.

302
00:25:27,167 --> 00:25:29,168
猛搓我那小香肠...
I skinned my sausage.

303
00:25:29,202 --> 00:25:32,404
猛揍我那爱哭的小秃子...
I made the bald man cry

304
00:25:32,439 --> 00:25:34,440
<i>给那炖海龟加了点作料,
into the turtle stew,</i>

305
00:25:34,475 --> 00:25:36,476
我相信我老姐把它吃了.
which I do believe my sister ate.

306
00:25:36,509 --> 00:25:38,445
<i>至少我希望她吃了.
At least I hope she did.</i>

307
00:25:38,478 --> 00:25:40,813
有一回我又带了一头公驴和一个蜂窝
Once I brought a jackass and a honeycomb

308
00:25:40,848 --> 00:25:43,015
- 去一家妓院... - 住口!
- into a brothel... - Silence!

309
00:25:43,048 --> 00:25:44,650
后来怎么样了?
What happened next?

310
00:25:45,651 --> 00:25:48,686
你以为你在干什么?
What do you think you're doing?

311
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:50,654
我在认罪啊.
Confessing my crimes.

312
00:25:50,688 --> 00:25:53,224
提利昂大人, 你被控
Lord Tyrion, you are accused

313
00:25:53,257 --> 00:25:56,727
雇人行刺我卧病在床的儿子布兰,
of hiring a man to slay my son Bran in his bed,

314
00:25:56,762 --> 00:25:59,564
<i>以及密谋害死我妹妹的丈夫
and of conspiring to murder my sister's husband</i>

315
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:03,436
琼恩艾林大人, 国王之手.
Lord Jon Arryn, the Hand of the King.

316
00:26:03,469 --> 00:26:05,804
哦, 我非常抱歉.
Oh, I'm very sorry.

317
00:26:06,974 --> 00:26:08,909
我对这些一无所知.
I don't know anything about all that.

318
00:26:10,044 --> 00:26:12,279
你的玩笑开够了.
You've had your little joke.

319
00:26:12,313 --> 00:26:14,682
我相信你玩得很愉快.
I trust you enjoyed it.

320
00:26:14,717 --> 00:26:17,585
莫德, 带他回地牢.
Mord, take him back to the dungeon.

321
00:26:17,620 --> 00:26:19,954
这次找个更小的房间...
But this time find a smaller cell...

322
00:26:19,988 --> 00:26:22,090
而且地板也更斜的.
With a steeper floor.

323
00:26:22,124 --> 00:26:24,892
难道这就是所谓
Is this how justice

324
00:26:24,927 --> 00:26:26,794
艾林谷的正义?
is done in the Vale?

325
00:26:26,829 --> 00:26:29,397
<i>你指控我有罪,
You accuse me of crimes,</i>

326
00:26:29,431 --> 00:26:32,600
我否认有罪, 所以你把我扔进牢房
I deny them, so you throw me into a cell

327
00:26:32,633 --> 00:26:34,502
<i>冻饿而死?
to freeze and starve?</i>

328
00:26:34,535 --> 00:26:37,471
国王的正义到哪里去了?
Where is the King's Justice?

329
00:26:37,506 --> 00:26:40,875
既然我遭到指控, 我要求公平审判!
I am accused and demand a trial!

330
00:26:42,611 --> 00:26:44,546
如果你被判有罪,
If you're tried and found guilty,

331
00:26:44,581 --> 00:26:47,683
那么依照国王的律法你只有死路一条.
then by the King's own laws you will pay with your life.

332
00:26:47,717 --> 00:26:50,821
我尊重律法.
I understand the law.

333
00:26:50,854 --> 00:26:53,422
我们鹰巢城没有刽子手.
We have no executioner in the Eyrie.

334
00:26:53,458 --> 00:26:56,259
我们这里有更文雅的法子.
Life is more elegant here.

335
00:26:56,294 --> 00:26:58,227
打开月门.
Open the moon door.

336
00:27:18,881 --> 00:27:21,850
<i>你想要一场审判, 兰尼斯特大人.
You want a trial, My Lord Lannister.</i>

337
00:27:21,883 --> 00:27:23,884
很好.
Very well.

338
00:27:23,919 --> 00:27:26,888
我儿子会倾听你要说的话,
My son will listen to whatever you have to say,

339
00:27:26,922 --> 00:27:29,189
而你将接受他的判决.
and you will hear his judgment.

340
00:27:29,225 --> 00:27:31,325
然后你就可以离开...
Then you will leave...

341
00:27:31,361 --> 00:27:33,495
从这道门或那道门.
By one door or the other.

342
00:27:33,528 --> 00:27:36,730
不必惊动罗宾大人了.
No need to bother Lord Robin.

343
00:27:36,765 --> 00:27:40,401
我要求比武审判.
I demand a trial by combat.

344
00:27:49,044 --> 00:27:50,911
你当然有这个权利.
You have that right.

345
00:27:51,980 --> 00:27:53,881
夫人, 我请您恩准.
My Lady, I beg the honor.

346
00:27:53,916 --> 00:27:55,883
让我做您的代理骑士.
Let me be your champion.

347
00:27:55,918 --> 00:27:58,319
