你是我亲爱的小姐.
You're My Lady.

532
00:41:55,306 --> 00:41:58,475
有朝一日我们会在朝堂上举行婚礼.
One day we'll be married in the throne room.

533
00:41:58,509 --> 00:42:02,444
七国各地的领主和夫人们都会赶来,
Lords and ladies from all over the Seven Kingdoms will come,

534
