and you will be Queen over all of them.

537
00:42:14,223 --> 00:42:16,658
<i>我永远不会再对你无礼.
I'll never disrespect you again.</i>

538
00:42:16,692 --> 00:42:19,895
我也永远不会再对你粗暴.
I'll never be cruel to you again.

539
00:42:19,928 --> 00:42:22,230
