from this day

542
00:42:29,806 --> 00:42:32,574
直到我生命的最后一天.
until my last day.

543
00:42:54,665 --> 00:42:56,766
停下.
Stop.

544
00:42:56,801 --> 00:42:59,370
- 停下! - 哦哇.
- Stop! - Whoa.

545
00:43:00,772 --> 00:43:03,306
- 你在干什么? - 去君临.
- What are you doing? - Going to King's Landing.

546
00:43:03,341 --> 00:43:05,442
乘一辆运芜菁的车子?
In a turnip cart?

547
00:43:05,475 --> 00:43:08,478
我会在白港找一条去南方的船.
I'll find a ship heading south in White Harbor.

548
00:43:09,545 --> 00:43:11,346
你付得起船钱吗?
And you can afford that?

549
00:43:11,381 --> 00:43:14,082
我的一些朋友比另一些慷慨.
Some of my friends are more generous than others.

550
