There's nothing left for me here.

564
00:43:48,152 --> 00:43:50,219
我们走吧, 斯特芬.
Let's go, Stefon.

565
00:43:50,254 --> 00:43:51,721
<i>走喽.
Giddyup.</i>

566
00:43:51,754 --> 00:43:54,022
让我再看一眼!
Let me see it one more time!

567
00:43:54,056 --> 00:43:56,357
看什么?
See what?

568
00:44:07,770 --> 00:44:09,870
我会想念你的.
I'm going to miss you.

569
00:44:09,906 --> 00:44:11,772
我知道.
I know.

570
00:44:25,553 --> 00:44:27,587
我要送你们俩回临冬城.
I'm sending you both back to Winterfell.

571
00:44:27,621 --> 00:44:29,022
- 什么?! - 听我说...
- What?! - Listen...

572
00:44:29,056 --> 00:44:31,658
- 乔佛里的事怎么办? - 因为你的腿伤好不了吗?
- What about Joffrey? - Are you dying because of your leg?

573
00:44:31,692 --> 00:44:32,971
<i>所以你要送我们回家?
Is that why you're sending us home?</i>

574
00:44:32,995 --> 00:44:34,160
什么? 不是.
What? No.

575
00:44:34,161 --> 00:44:35,594
求你了, 父亲. 不要.
Please, father. Please don't.

576
00:44:35,629 --> 00:44:37,797
不可以. 我要跟西利欧上课.
You can't. I've got my lessons with Syrio.

577
00:44:37,830 --> 00:44:39,431
我一定会表现好的.
I'm finally getting good.

578
00:44:39,466 --> 00:44:41,900
这不是在惩罚你们.
This isn't a punishment.

579
00:44:41,935 --> 00:44:44,337
我让你们回临冬城是为你们的安全着想.
I want you back in Winterfell for your own safety.

580
00:44:44,370 --> 00:44:45,804
我们可以带西利欧一起走吗?
Can we take Syrio back with us?

581
00:44:45,839 --> 00:44:47,411
谁管你的笨舞蹈老师啊?
Who cares about your stupid dancing teacher?

582
00:44:47,435 --> 00:44:48,736
