I can't go.

583
00:44:48,743 --> 00:44:50,611
我是要嫁给乔佛里王子的.
I'm supposed to marry Prince Joffrey.

584
00:44:50,645 --> 00:44:52,547
我爱他, 我要做他的王后
I love him and I'm meant to be his Queen

585
00:44:52,580 --> 00:44:55,183
- 为他生孩子. - 七层地狱啊.
- and have his babies. - Seven hells.

586
00:44:55,216 --> 00:44:56,850
等你再大点,
When you're old enough,

587
00:44:56,884 --> 00:44:59,587
我会给你找个配得上你的人,
I'll make you a match with someone who's worthy of you,

588
00:44:59,621 --> 00:45:02,290
既勇敢又温柔又强壮...
someone who's brave and gentle and strong...

589
00:45:02,324 --> 00:45:05,594
我不要什么勇敢温柔又强壮的人. 我只要他!
I don't want someone brave and gentle and strong. I want him!

590
00:45:05,627 --> 00:45:08,397
他会成为最伟大的国王, 如同黄金雄狮,
He'll be the greatest King that ever was, a golden lion,

591
00:45:08,431 --> 00:45:11,199
我会为她生下拥有漂亮金发的儿女.
and I'll give him sons with beautiful blond hair.

592
00:45:11,234 --> 00:45:13,868
<i>他才不是狮子, 白痴.
The lion'sot s Sigil, idiot.</i>

593
00:45:13,902 --> 00:45:15,703
他是鹿, 象他父亲一样.
He's a stag, like his father.

594
00:45:15,737 --> 00:45:18,640
他才不是. 他一点也不象那个酒鬼国王.
He is not. He's nothing like that old drunk King.

595
00:45:21,844 --> 00:45:24,679
去吧, 孩子们. 让修女帮你们收拾东西.
Go on, girls. Get your Septa and start packing your things.

596
00:45:24,714 --> 00:45:26,216
- 等等! - 来吧.
