Stop him.

608
00:47:12,660 --> 00:47:14,194
<i>她在哪儿?
Where is she?</i>

609
00:47:14,228 --> 00:47:16,362
<i>嗯?
Hmm?</i>

610
00:47:18,832 --> 00:47:21,600
