Where is she? I'm here for the feast.

611
00:47:22,670 --> 00:47:24,937
- 那烂女人的宴会? - 来.
- The whore's feast? - Come.

612
00:47:24,971 --> 00:47:26,638
把你的手拿开!
Get your hands off me!

613
00:47:26,672 --> 00:47:29,207
谁也不能触碰真龙!
No one touches the Dragon!

614
00:47:30,076 --> 00:47:32,243
<i>(酸腿国王!)
Khal rhae mhar!</i>

615
00:47:32,277 --> 00:47:35,045
