He says yes.

642
00:49:27,094 --> 00:49:29,995
你将拥有一顶黄金王冠...
You shall have a golden crown...

643
00:49:31,632 --> 00:49:34,199
任谁看了都会颤抖.
That men shall tremble to behold.

644
00:49:45,344 --> 00:49:47,545
我要的就只是这个.
That was all I wanted.

645
00:49:49,915 --> 00:49:52,049
