Ammeni haz jolin!</i>

652
00:50:33,960 --> 00:50:36,263
- 请你转过头, 卡丽熙. - 不.
- Look away, Khaleesi. - No.

653
00:50:43,237 --> 00:50:45,605
<i>不, 丹妮.
No, dany.</i>

654
00:50:45,638 --> 00:50:47,105
丹妮, 告诉他们.
Dany, tell them.

655
00:50:47,140 --> 00:50:48,574
告诉他们!
Make them!

656
00:50:49,576 --> 00:50:52,344
<i>丹妮, 让他们...
Dany, make them...</i>

657
00:50:54,013 --> 00:50:56,114
不, 你不能!
No, you can't!

658
00:50:56,149 --> 00:50:59,285
只要... 求你了!
Just... please!

659
00:50:59,319 --> 00:51:02,254
丹妮, 求你了!
Dany, please!

660
00:51:03,857 --> 00:51:06,359
国王的王冠.
A crown for a King.

661
00:51:21,341 --> 00:51:23,710
卡丽熙?
Khaleesi?

662
00:51:23,743 --> 00:51:25,946
他不是真龙.
He was no Dragon.

